{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1782829126.686474", "card_id": "Q_2055222122289558459", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 243}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日元跌破 1 美元兑 162 日元关口，创下近 40 年来新低，日本央行已加息至 1%，为何完全挡不住日元贬值颓势？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "日元兑美元汇率创下近 40 年来新低 6 月 30 日，日元跌破 1 美元兑 162 日元关口，触及 1986 年以来的最低水平。有日本学者指出，由于成本推动型通胀、人口压力以及日元与美元存在较大利差等因素的存在，日元走势疲软。日本内阁官房长官木原稔表示，将根据需要对外汇采取适当行动。 日本央行加息至 1%，为 1995 年以来最高水平 日本央行打出了约 30 年来的最猛加息拳，6 月 16 日，日本央行如期宣布加息 25 个基点，将政策利率从 0.75% 上调至 1% 水平，为 31 年来最高水平。日本央行以 7 票对 1 票作出利率决定。此前，日本央行已连续三次会议维持利率不变。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-cad75b6ec2b5f70b5df62deeda90e238_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "754 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2055222122289558459"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI9s6k29e52vEdEAMaCTEyMDIxNzUxMyCiuYzSBjAAOLgFQAByEzIwNTUyMjIxMjIyODk1NTg0NTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1782829126.687676", "card_id": "Q_2055040930516824522", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 83}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 deepseek2026 年 6 月 29 日再次调整收费标准？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-07f913d2b49bde68b0d4b18894fb1115.jpg?source=1a5df958"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "539 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2055040930516824522"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI9s6k29e52vEdEAMaCTEyMDIxMjU2OSDi54nSBjAAOJACQAFyEzIwNTUwNDA5MzA1MTY4MjQ1MjJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1782829126.688109", "card_id": "Q_2055052533110937112", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待外网热议 OR 上的热门匿名模型 Owl Alpha 被爆来自中国？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2a1613703af777a6cf23d6dced42e7c2.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "299 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2055052533110937112"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI9s6k29e52vEdEAMaCTEyMDIxMzA2OCCw/YnSBjAAOIQCQAJyEzIwNTUwNTI1MzMxMTA5MzcxMTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1782829126.688496", "card_id": "Q_2054901718014488895", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 54}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "网友称玻璃吸管碰到杯底易产生肉眼难见的微裂纹，会致吸入细渣划伤消化道，是这样吗？玻璃吸管到底安不安全？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "之所以不用用玻璃吸管喝水，那是因为玻璃吸管一旦撞到杯壁或杯底就会形成细小的玻璃裂纹，然后慢慢扩散直至破碎，那些碎碎的玻璃渣会随着水流吸入身体内，就连胃酸都无法分解它们，这样就会随时伤到我们的胃部、肠道。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-aa4a17158f55b3e91133bf3f2cd84bbd.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "217 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2054901718014488895"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI9s6k29e52vEdEAMaCTEyMDIwMzg5MyC75IfSBjAAOJ4BQANyEzIwNTQ5MDE3MTgwMTQ0ODg4OTV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1782829126.689296", "card_id": "Q_2055324594878113683", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 65}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "湖北 702 分考生放弃清北选择南大计算机，如何看待他的选择？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "6 月 28 日，湖北省武昌实验中学学生王昕博得知了自己高考具体分数，702 分，其中语文 142 分高分，数学 143 分，英语 144 分。 在分数足够报清北的情况下，他选择南京大学计算机相关专业。 「为什么没有选择清北？」王昕博首先给出专业上的理由：「南京大学本身就是一个计算机科学优势很大的学校，在这一领域的资源比较丰厚。」 这个选择并非临时起意。王昕博对计算机的兴趣从高中开始便已扎根。高一高二时，他投身信息学竞赛，并在全国青少年信息学奥林匹克竞赛（NOI）中摘得铜牌。「未来这个行业会对整个世界产生巨大的影响，所以我也想投身于这一时代潮流。」他说。王昕博高考 702 分，没有选择清北 | 极目新闻 反向问题：去年一位考生考入南大计算机，为清北梦顶着巨大压力选择复读一年。考入南大计算机，复读考清北值吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7f06a019d93dcd7b43b6012db6576370_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "194 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2055324594878113683"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI9s6k29e52vEdEAMaCTEyMDIyNjIzNCCR+I3SBjAAOHVABHITMjA1NTMyNDU5NDg3ODExMzY4M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1782829126.690527", "card_id": "Q_2048064764694245412", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 105}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果把《爱情公寓》放到现在，它还是年轻人理想中的合租生活吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "《爱情公寓》曾经塑造了一种很理想化的合租想象：朋友住在一起，客厅很大，随时有人聊天，生活热闹又有趣。但现实中的合租，往往还要面对房租分摊、公共卫生、作息差异、边界感、厨房使用、室友更替等问题。 如果把这种合租模式放到今天的城市租房现实里，它还成立吗？年轻人现在还向往这种合租生活，还是更想拥有一个安静、稳定、边界清楚的小空间？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-e5a1d429fbd151e8a187c855d7c42b9b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "191 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2048064764694245412"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI9s6k29e52vEdEAMaCTExOTkxMzgxNCDTpaTRBjAAOMQBQAVyEzIwNDgwNjQ3NjQ2OTQyNDU0MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1782829126.691021", "card_id": "Q_2055214660853266021", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 124}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "博主爆料明星集体失业成常态，流量明星无戏可拍，目前影视行业现状到底怎么样？"}, "excerp